quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  60,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  60,1,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum meri raah mein jehaad karne ke liye aur meri Raza joi ki khatir ( watan chore kar gharon se ) niklay ho to mere aur apne dushmanon ko dost nah banaao tum unn ke sath dosti ki terhan daaltay ho, halaank jo haq tumahray paas aaya hai uss ko maan-ne se woh inkaar kar chuke hain aur unn ki rawish yeh hai ke rasool ko aur khud tum ko sirf iss qasoor par jala watan karte hain ke tum apne rab, Allah par imaan laaye ho tum chhupa kar unn ko dostana pegham bhaijtay ho, halaank jo kuch tum chhupa kar karte ho aur jo alania karte ho, har cheez ko mein khoob jaanta hon jo shakhs bhi tum mein se aisa kere woh yaqeenan raah raast se bhatak gaya"
  60,2,unn ka rawayya to yeh hai ke agar tum par qaboo pa jayen to tumahray sath dushmani karen aur haath aur zabaan se tumhe azaar den woh to yeh chahtay hain ke tum kisi terhan kafir ho jao
  60,3,"qayamat ke din nah tumhari rishta dariyan kisi kaam ayen gi nah tumhari aulaad uss roz Allah tumahray darmain judai daal day ga, aur o hi tumahray aamaal ka dekhnay wala hai"
  60,4,"tum logon ke liye ibrahim aur uss ke sathiyon mein aik acha namona hai ke onhon ne apni qoum se saaf keh diya"" hum tum se aur tumahray inn mabodon se jin ko tum khuda ko chore kar pujte ho qatee bezaar hain, hum ne tum se kufar kya aur hamaray aur tumahray darmain hamesha ke liye adawat ho gayi aur bair par gaya jab taq tum Allah wahid par imaan nah lao"" magar ibrahim ka apne baap se yeh kehna ( iss se mustasna hai ) ke"" mein aap ke liye mughfirat ki darkhwast zaroor karoon ga, aur Allah se aap ke liye kuch haasil kar lena mere bas mein nahi hai"" ( aur ibrahim o ashaab ibrahim ki dua yeh thi ke )"" ae hamaray rab, tairay hi oopar hum ne bhrosa kya aur teri hi taraf hum ne rujoo kar liya aur tairay hi huzoor hamein palatna hai"
  60,5,"ae hamaray rab, hamein kafiroon ke liye fitnah nah bana day aur ae hamaray rab, hamarayKasoroo-n se dar guzar farma, be shak to hi zabardast aur Dana hai """
  60,6,aِnhi logon ke tarz amal mein tumahray liye aur har uss shakhs ke liye acha namona hai jo Allah aur roz aakhir ka umeed waar ho iss se koi munharif ho to Allah be niaz aur apni zaat mein aap Mahmood hai
  60,7,baeed nahi ke Allah kabhi tumahray aur unn logon ke darmain mohabbat daal day jin se aaj tum ne dushmani mol li hai Allah barri qudrat rakhta hai aur woh ghafoor o Raheem hai
  60,8,Allah tmin is baat se nahi rokta ke tum un logon ke sath neki aur insaaf ka bartao karo jinhon ne deen ke maamla mein tum se jung nahi ki hai aur tumhe tumahray gharon se nahi nikala hai Allah insaaf karne walon ko pasand karta hai
  60,9,woh tumhe jis baat se rokta hai woh to yeh hai ke tum unn logon se dosti karo jinhon ne tum se deen ke maamla mein jung ki hai aur tumhe tumahray gharon se nikala hai aur tumahray ikhraj mein aik dosray ki madad ki hai unn se jo log dosti karen wohi zalim hain
  60,10,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab momin aurtain hijrat kar ke tumahray paas ayen to ( un ke momin honay ki ) jaanch partaal kar lau, aur un ke imaan ki haqeeqat Allah hi behtar jaanta hai phir jab tumhe maloom ho jaye ke woh momin hain to inhen kufar ki taraf wapas nah karo nah woh kufar ke liye halal hain aur nah kufar un ke liye halal un ke kafir shoharon ne jo mohar unn ko diye thay woh inhen phair do aur un se nikah kar lainay mein tum par koi gunah nahi jabkay tum unn ke mohar unn ko ada kar do aur tum khud bhi kafir aurton ko apne nikah mein nah rokay raho jo mohar tum ne apni kafir biwion ko diye thay woh tum wapas maang lau aur jo mohar kafiroon ne apni musalman biwion ko diye thay inhen woh wapas maang len yeh Allah ka hukum hai, woh tumahray darmain faisla karta hai aur Allah Aleem o hakeem hai"
  60,11,aur agar tumhari kafir biwion ke muhroon mein se kuch tumhe kufar se wapas nah miley aur phir tumhari nobat aeye to jin logon ki biwiyan idhar reh gayi hain unn ko itni raqam ada kar do jo unn ke diye hue muhroon ke barabar ho aur uss khuda se dar te raho jis par tum imaan laaye ho
  60,12,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jab tumahray paas momin aurtain baet karne ke liye ayen aur is baat ka ehad karen ke woh Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko shareek nah karen gi, chori nah karen gi, zina nah karen gi, apni aulaad ko qatal nah karen gi, apne haath paon ke agay koi bohtan ghurr kar nah layein gi, aur kisi amar Maroof mein tumhari nafarmani nah karen gi, to un se baet le lau aur unn ke haq mein Allah se duaye mughfirat karo, yaqeenan Allah dar guzar frmane wala aur reham karne wala hai"
  60,13,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, unn logon ko dost nah banaao jin par Allah ne ghazab farmaya hai, jo akhirat se isi terhan mayoos hain jis terhan qabron mein parre hue kafir mayoos hain"
